data.description: Priced in a range between $699,000 to $749,000. Amazing views of  El Capitan coupled with privacy. This beautiful home is on a large parcel on public sewer you wouldn't expect to find in a location so close to shopping centers, supermarket, health clubs, gyms, and coffee shops.  One of Lakesides best locations with easy freeway access to highways 67,52,125 and 8.  Hard to find location in the sought after Wintergardens/Woodside area. This home features open concept single level living with plenty of parking for your RV, Boat and toys as well as a 2-car garage. Award winning schools. Once this is sold you may spend years hoping to find all this home has to offer.
